Seems to be about 2x faster than pivoted QR for a large underdetermined solve, with similar accuracy (assuming full row rank):
```jl
julia> A = rand(1000,1500); b = rand(size(A,1));

julia> @btime lq($A) \ $b;
  101.955 ms (14 allocations: 19.37 MiB)

julia> @btime qr($A, Val{true}()) \ $b;
  250.584 ms (8046 allocations: 31.98 MiB)

julia> x = lq(A) \ b; norm(x - qr(A, Val{true}()) \ b) / norm(x)
3.5357944054772334e-15
```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/34350/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/34350/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2464699560","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/34350#issuecomment-2464699560","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/34350","id":2464699560,"node_id":"IC_kwDOABkWpM6S6FSo","user":{"login":"dkarrasch","id":26658441,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI2NjU4NDQx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26658441?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch","html_url":"https://github.com/dkarrasch","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dkarrasch/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-11-08T13:01:00Z","updated_at":"2024-11-08T13:01:00Z","author_association":"MEMBER","body":"Currently, we only distinguish square from non-square, right? Sounds like a good idea.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/2464699560/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null